{
  "stem": "27390.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you can imagine the-- the-- the joy that he was saved.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He wasn't deported.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And after that, my-- my brother and my mother managed to get a job, because we could see, whoever's not working doesn't stand a chance.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were hoping, if you're working-- he kept saying, if you're working, nothing will happen to you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This was his favorite slogan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Work saves you from all the trouble.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If you're working, nothing will happen to you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So they managed to get jobs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My mother started working in a-- in a place where they sorted clothes, old clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My brother got a job in a metal factory, where they made all different kinds of machine tools.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He learned.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They taught him how to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The clothes that my mother worked was-- they were bringing in tons and tons of-- of clothes from people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We didn't know where these clothes was coming from.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my mother was not allowed to say anything about her job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That's another thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "If-- if there-- if somebody-- if a rumor went around, and the police found out, from where this rumor originated, these people were picked up, right away, and were deported.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So if-- even if you knew something, what's going on, you had to keep it to yourself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You were not allowed to tell anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But one day, I remember my mother came home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she said, she found a-- a-- a-- a note in-- in one of the clothes that they sorted.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And it said that the-- a man wrote it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he said, we are queuing up now to go to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we want-- you know, I'm writing this note.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "People should know what's happening to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
